Package: python3-truenas-pyos
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: TrueNAS OS utilities
 This package provides Python bindings for TrueNAS OS-specific utilities
 and system operations. It includes functions for working with mount points,
 file handles, and other low-level system operations required by TrueNAS.
